metadata.name: Orange Juice
metadata.description:
GM. Enjoy a nice glass of OJ first thing in the morning.

Starting with Orange Juice, our base flavor/token, you may mint according to the burn mechanism in the following days.

On specified days, you may burn your Orange Juice and change the flavor of your Juicebox according. On the final day, there will be an increased burn to claim the secret flavor.

Once the flavor change has passed, there will be one final surprise burn so don't be shy on your flavor allocations ðŸ˜‰

Remember, it never hurts to stay hydrated!
